OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779444433
OL,3,CSlight improvement in consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence amid 'clear challenges
OL,5,Cahead'
OL,7,FA fall in inflation led to a slight
OL,8,Fimprovement in consumer confidence
OL,9,Fthis month amid warnings of "clear
OL,10,Fchallenges ahead".
OL,12,FGfK's long-running Consumer Confidence
OL,13,FIndex rose by two points in May, but
OL,14,Fis still four points lower than this
OL,15,Ftime last year at minus 23.
OL,26,@qD@]OUrD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
