OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779444433
OL,3,CSlight improvement in consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence amid 'clear challenges
OL,5,Cahead'
OL,7,FDespite confidence in the general
OL,8,Feconomy over the coming year rising
OL,9,Ffive points, it remains five points
OL,10,Flower than last May at minus 38, while
OL,11,Fconfidence in personal finances over
OL,12,Fthe next 12 months is up two points to
OL,13,Fminus two, four points down on a year
OL,14,Fago.
OL,16,FThe major purchase index, an indicator
OL,17,Fof confidence in buying big ticket
OL,18,Fitems, dropped two points to minus 20,
OL,19,Ffour points lower than May last year
OL,20,Fand its lowest level since last
OL,21,FJanuary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779444433
OL,3,CSlight improvement in consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence amid 'clear challenges
OL,5,Cahead'
OL,7,FKey income groups recorded "more
OL,8,Fworrying" major purchase scores, with
OL,9,Fconfidence among those earning between
OL,10,F#14,500 and #24,999 posting a 19-point
OL,11,Fdrop to minus 33.
OL,13,FSimilarly, there was a steep fall
OL,14,Fwithin the average household income
OL,15,Fgroup earning between #35,000 and
OL,16,F#49,999, with a 10-point drop to minus
OL,17,F27.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
