OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779444433
OL,3,CSlight improvement in consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence amid 'clear challenges
OL,5,Cahead'
OL,7,FNeil Bellamy, consumer insights
OL,8,Fdirector at GfK, said: "Consumers
OL,9,Fappear to be in a more generous mood
OL,10,Fin May, with a two-point increase in
OL,11,Fthe headline score and improving
OL,12,Fperceptions of both personal finances
OL,13,Fand the wider economy.
OL,15,F"Clearly, for specific groups of
OL,16,Fconsumers, the impact of cost-of-
OL,17,Fliving pressures are acute.
OL,26,@pD@XOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779444433
OL,3,CSlight improvement in consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence amid 'clear challenges
OL,5,Cahead'
OL,7,F"Moreover, our savings measure ` down
OL,8,Fby the unusually high amount of 10
OL,9,Fpoints ` suggests people are diverting
OL,10,Ffunds from savings accounts to pay for
OL,11,Fday-to-day expenses.
OL,13,F"Inflation may have fallen in April,
OL,14,Fbut with price pressures expected to
OL,15,Frise again and continued uncertainty
OL,16,Faround interest rates, it's unlikely
OL,17,FMay marks the beginning of a sustained
OL,18,Fimprovement."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@MO]
